167
00:09:58,260 --> 00:09:58,780
Why?

168
00:09:59,140 --> 00:09:59,900
Has the Academy become

169
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,140
so shameless now?

170
00:10:01,740 --> 00:10:03,380
Is leaking exam questions in advance

171
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:05,500
