true strengths are tested.

181
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:20,220
The preliminary examination is just

182
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:22,020
for the young men

183
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,300
to bring home some good omens.

184
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,300
Don't take it so seriously, Liuyue.

185
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,380
Mr. Zhuomo is right.

186
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,780
Moreover,

187
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,580
with Mr. Liuyue's talent,

188
