Yes, I'm threatening you.

221
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:28,860
So what?

222
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:29,900
You do know

223
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:31,580
I'm very talkative.

224
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:32,140
I'll go

225
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:32,860
to Master every day

226
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:33,620
