231
00:11:39,020 --> 00:11:39,820
and agrees

232
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:40,900
to make you the chief examiner

233
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,340
year after year.

234
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:42,700
Fine.

235
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,540
Year after year.

236
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:45,500
I surrender.

