Beyond civil and military.

238
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:04,260
That's right.

239
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:05,980
It's beyond civil and military.

240
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:09,020
Major exams in the world are divided
into civil and military categories.

241
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:11,100
But there are so many interesting things

242
00:12:11,380 --> 00:12:13,140
beyond these two categories.

243
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,260
So

244
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,500
I won't test civil

245
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,540
or military subjects.

246
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:19,660
