250
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:27,780
This is worse than saying nothing.

251
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:29,860
But what exactly is tested

252
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,260
if it has nothing to do
with civil and military subjects.

253
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:32,860
You need to know

254
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,500
that our academy not only seeks people

255
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:35,740
who excel

256
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:36,780
in both civil and military skills

257
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,860
but also those who are interesting.

258
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,140
My topic is to test

259
