264
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,740
What I said was
from the bottom of my heart

265
00:12:57,900 --> 00:12:59,340
and has nothing to do

266
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,500
with the friend you brought.

267
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:02,740
